1.title: We're Back, and We're Pregnant!
1.plot: In the final season opener, Snooki and JWoww (both pregnant) become neighbors for the summer. Roger and Jionni become closer than they ever imagined when they accidentally attend a birthing class together.

2.title: That's Not Very Namaste of You
2.plot: The girls try to relax with pre-natal yoga while Jionni is tormented by Lorenzo's "terrible twos". Snooki throws JWoww a surprise baby shower and serves up some disturbing cakes.

3.title: And Baby Makes Six
3.plot: Snooki helps Jenni prepare for her baby's arrival; Jionni warns Roger about the delivery; Jenni goes into labor and changes her mind about the epidural.

4.title: Welcome Home, Meilani!
4.plot: Jenni and Roger get used to life as new parents; Snooki and Jionni plan an elaborate welcome home party for Meilani.

5.title: Got Gatsby?
5.plot: Exhaustion takes its toll on new parents JWoww and Roger. Snooki turns into a bridezilla while planning her Gatsby-themed bridal shower.

6.title: I Feel Like a Pregnant Virgin
6.plot: Snooki shows off her wedding gown to JWoww. Jionni's parents visit town while new parenthood starts to cause problems for JWoww and Roger.

7.title: Little Hos on the Prairie
7.plot: Jenni and Roger work through issues with being new parents; Snooki and Jionni have a garden war; Jenni throws Snooki a high tea bridal luncheon.

8.title: Summer's Over... Back to the Basement
8.plot: Jenni gets a makeover and takes her family on a camping trip; Snooki and Jionni begin to decorate their new house.

9.title: Dear Snooki & Jwoww
9.plot: JWoww gets a mommy makeover and takes her family camping. Snooki and Jionni start decorating their house but can't move in until the house is finished.

11.title: Fashion Fun Fun Fun Special
11.plot: Snooki and Jenni review the evolution of their style from their partying days at the Jersey Shore to the present day.

12.title: It's Like a Rollercoaster of Pain
12.plot: Snooki and Jionni are eager to move into the new house before the baby is born; Jenni and Janis throw Snooki a surprise sprinkle party.

13.title: Welcome Home, Giovanna
13.plot: Snooki gives birth to her daughter; Jenni and Snooki decide to pamper the fathers during a "daddy appreciation day"; Snooki and Jionni move into their home.

14.title: It's My Bachelorette Party... I'm Single and Ready to Mingle!
14.plot: Things get crazy for Snooki and Jionni when they travel to Miami for bachelor and bachelorette parties.

15.title: I Do. Now What?
15.plot: JWoww and Roger have a christening for Meilani. It's the big day for Snooki as she walks down the aisle and marries Jionni. As they celebrate how far they have come, the girls look back.

0.title: BTS Photoshoot
0.plot: Take a peek behind the scenes at the photoshoot for Snooki & Jwoww's brand new show!

1.title: Sorry Neighbors, Cause These Bitches Are Moving In
1.plot: Jersey Shore BFF's, Snooki and JWoww, decide it's time they move in together and have one last hurrah before their relationships back home get too serious, but Snooki's two big secrets for Jwoww will change everything.

2.title: What Did I Get Myself Into?
2.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Even though Snooki is pregnant and engaged, she and Jwoww still agree to move in together. But when Jionni and Roger come over for the first time, a fight erupts over the bachelor party.

3.title: It Looks Like a Little Meatball
3.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Snooki has her first ultrasound to see if the baby is healthy. Snooki and Jwoww settle in and decorate their new digs.

4.title: Guess Who's Coming to Dinner
4.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Snooki and JWoww invite their Jersey Shore roommates over for dinner so Snooki can reveal her big news, but first, a raunchy handyman almost ruins their plans for getting the place ready on time.

5.title: Sober Party of One
5.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. The Jersey Shore roommates give Snooki a hard time for being pregnant and engaged. JWoww and Snooki throw a housewarming party for their friends and family.

6.title: Calm Down Hormonal!
6.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Snooki volunteers at a doggie daycare. JWoww makes a new friend at a cooking class, which annoys Snooki. Roger and JWoww's relationship begins to crumble.

7.title: Meet the In-Laws
7.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. JWoww and Roger continue to fight. The girls surprise Jionni and Roger by taking them to a Drag Show. Snooki and Jionni have an engagement dinner with their families.

8.title: Cancun Is Not an Island
8.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. The girls head to Cancun for vacation. JWoww lets loose while Snooki finds it difficult to relax during her pregnancy. The girls bicker about late night plans, while a fight in a club puts Snooki in an uncomfortable situation.

9.title: Sitting Alone in a Hotel Room Sucks
9.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. JWoww and Snooki's friendship is tested on their last night in Cancun. Back in Jersey City, Roger and JWoww hit another rocky patch while Snooki questions her engagement.

10.title: Couples Hell
10.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Roger and JWoww consider the future of their relationship while Snooki and Jionni fight about a picture on Twitter, instead of celebrating Jionni's birthday.

11.title: My Baby Is Boring!
11.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Snooki and Jwoww get a taste of motherhood when they care for two fake babies, and Snooki finds out the gender of her real baby.

13.title: The End?
13.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. In order to get answers to some important questions, Snooki and Jwoww swap boyfriends for the night. The girls must decide if they are going to stay in Jersey City or move home with their boyfriends.

1.title: New Beginnings
1.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. While Snooki and Jionni prepare for parenthood, JWoww settles into un-married life with Roger. Snooki has a baby shower.

2.title: Pregnant Problems
2.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. As her due date draws near, Snooki begins to feel overwhelmed with her pregnancy. JWoww not so subtly hints that it is time for Roger to propose and she wants a big fat ring.

3.title: Last Call at Club Uterus
3.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. JWoww's Dad hits on one of her friends at a family BBQ. Snooki goes into labor early. Lorenzo is born.

4.title: Now What?
4.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Snooki and Jionni settle in to life as new parents. JWoww and Roger head up to Maine to visit his family.

5.title: Maine Squeeze
5.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. JWoww tries to show Roger that she can be an outdoor girl in Maine. Snooki and Jionni realize that being parents is more exhausting than they thought. Roger reveals a secret.

6.title: The Honeymoon Is Over
6.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Roger and JWoww's trip to Maine solidifies his feelings for her...and then they get into a fight. And being new parents begins to take its toll on Snooki and Jionni's relationship.

7.title: Turning Over a New League
7.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Snooki and Jionni try to get their relationship back on track. JWoww considers introducing Roger to her Mother.

8.title: Between a Rock and a Hard Place
8.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Nicole and Jionni go on their first date since having the baby, Roger goes engagement ring shopping, and JWoww gets an indecent proposal.

9.title: Taking the Plunge
9.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Roger proposes to JWoww, but before he makes it official, he has some tricks up his sleeve.

10.title: I'm a Good Fiancé and I'm a Mom!
10.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Jionni and Roger celebrate fatherhood at a Dadchelor Party. And Nicole and JWoww outdo the boys on a wild girls' night out.

11.title: I Might Not Be Engaged After This
11.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. The honeymoon is over! The aftermath of Girl's night out brings both couples to the verge of breaking up.

12.title: All's Well That Ends Well?
12.plot: Watch an all new season of Snooki & Jwoww Tuesdays at 10p/9c on MTV. Snooki and JWoww try to salvage their relationships before it's too late. The Jersey Shore roommates help celebrate JWoww and Roger's engagement.

13.title: Besties, Babies & Big A... Rings
13.plot: A look back at the last two seasons of Snooki & JWoww living together, living with their men, and living it up including outtakes and never-before-seen footage.

1.title: We're Back B...
1.plot: Snooki and Jionni are scared to tell Jionni's Mom that they got a shore house for the summer. JWoww tries to salvage her relationship with Roger by trying to get him to go to couples therapy.

2.title: Movin on Up!
2.plot: Snooki and Jionni move out of the basement at Jionni's parents house. Jenni works on training her dogs to become service animals.

3.title: Mommy
3.plot: Snooki searches for a babysitter for Lorenzo; Jenni and Roger take Snooki and Jionni to the haunted Pennhurst Asylum.

4.title: Liars!
4.plot: Jenni and Snooki drive to Atlantic City for a girls weekend getaway. Jionnoi is left to watch Lorenzo but ends up leaving the baby with Janis so he and Roger can go paintballing.

5.title: I Want a Veil!
5.plot: While Jenni and Snooki are shopping for wedding dresses, Jenni comes to the conclusion that she's ready for marriage.

6.title: Let the Planning Begin!
6.plot: Snooki realizes she is in over her head when it comes to wedding planning after visiting wedding venues with Jionni. JWoww and Roger go to an adoption fair hoping to learn more about the process.

7.title: Baby Boot Camp
7.plot: Jenni wants to see how good of a father Roger will be so Snooki and Jenni put Roger through baby boot camp. Jionni and Roger go on the hunt to purchase a swing set for Lorenzo.

8.title: Oui Can Cook!
8.plot: Snooki and JWoww help out at a charity dog wash. Roger and Jionni plan a romantic French dinner for the girls. Snooki takes a DNA test.

9.title: Welcome to the Dude Ranch!
9.plot: The gang heads out for a couples weekend at a Dude Ranch. The girls are hoping for a romantic getaway, but instead they get pranked non-stop by Roger and Jionni.

10.title: What a Drag!
10.plot: Snooki reviews the results of her DNA test. Jenni's dogs take their last test to recieve their service animal certificate. Jenni invites the Joey's over to have a drag party.

11.title: Couples Weekend
11.plot: Snooki and Jenni invite their Jersey Shore roommates over for a couples weekend.

12.title: Enzo's 1st Birthday
12.plot: Snooki and Jionni celebrate Lorenzo's first birthday with Roger and Jenni. Snooki get's exciting new about Dancing with the Stars.

13.title: The Not Yet Wed Game
13.plot: Snooki, Jenni, Jionni, and Roger play a game to see who knows each other best.

imdb.plot outline: An inside look of reality show personalities Nicole 'Snooki' Polizzi and husband Jionni LaValle, Jenni 'JWOWW' Farley and Fiancé Roger Matthews as they live their lives together as best friends, and also reality stars. Nicole and Jenni are best friends and their signifcant others have also become friends through the years. Experience their lives from friends living together in Season 1, to being either a mother of two (Nicole) or a new mom (Jenni) in Season 4, the finale season. See how the two are ablt to balence their 'BFF' relationship, their own relationships, and family life. Watch how their lives have changed from what they were in the years of "Jersey Shore." The show has four season, and the fourth season will be the last, it premiered on June 21st, 2012, and its final season premired on November 5th, 2014. Recording of the fourth and final season continues into november 2014, with recording starting a few weeks before the birth of Jenni ''JWOWW' and Roger's child, Meilani Alexandra Matthews on July 13th, 2014. The fourth season also features events like Nicole 'Snooki' and Jionni's birth of a second child, Giovanna Marie LaValle, younger sister of Lorenzo Dominic LaValle born on August 26th, 2012, and Nicole 'Snooki' and Jionni's Bachelor/bachelorette parties in Miami, and also their wedding, which was on November 29th, 2014. In the first season Nicole 'Snooki' and Jenni 'JWOWW' shared an apartment on Mercer Street in Jersey City, New Jersey. Season two brought both back to where they usually live and was all about the birth of Lorenzo and Nicole 'Snooki' and Jionni becoming new parents, and Jenni 'JWOWW' and Roger taking more steps to make a stronger relationship while also thinking about their future. Season three brings the two closer with Nicole 'Snooki' and Jionni renting a house on the Jersey Shore just minutes from where Jenni 'JWOWW' and Roger live. It showed Nicole 'Snooki' and Jionni getting used to parenthood as Lorenzo was almost a year old at the time, and Jenni 'JWOWW' and Roger fixing the issues in their relationship and being to think about starting a family in the future, and including adoption as a very likely choice for the couple. Season four has brought Besties Nicole 'Snooki' and Jenni 'JWOWW' to live right next to each other in Manchester, New Jersey. Nicole 'Snooki' and Jionni rented a house next door to Jenni 'JWOWW' and Rogers house, but have sinced moved into their brand new house in northern New Jersey. Snooki and JWOWW airs on Wednesday nights at 10:00/9:00c on MTV.
